data.description: Located in the desirable Pennypack neighborhood in Northeast Philadelphia, you'll find a tight-knit community where neighbors become friends. Enjoy the convenience of nearby parks, schools, shopping, and easy access to public transportation. Explore the local dining scene, take a stroll in the green spaces, and experience the true meaning of a comfortable and convenient lifestyle. Step into a warm and inviting living space, where natural light floods the room, creating a cozy atmosphere. The open concept kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting modern appliances and plenty of counter space. Venture out to your backyard oasis, offering endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment such as outdoor gatherings, gardening, and playtime. The three bedrooms, accompanied by two full bathrooms, offer ample space, providing comfort and versatility. The possibilities are endless; tailor these rooms to fit your lifestyle. Consider creating a home office for remote work, a delightful playroom for the little ones, or a cozy guest bedroom for visiting family and friends. With such flexibility, these rooms are ready to adapt to meet your ever-evolving needs. Additional features include a huge basement with laundry, ample storage, and the potential to be transformed into an additional living space. Plus, with parking for up to four cars, you'll never have to worry about finding space for your vehicles. Arrange your showing to experience the unique charm of this home firsthand!
